{"article_id":"rsP0tCZEb0n7IsBZ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON-House Speaker Paul Ryan said Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"he would retire at the end of the term ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"sparking an intraparty battle","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to succeed him","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and rattling Republicans","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"who expect a fierce struggle","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"to maintain their majority .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Less than three years into his tenure as speaker , Mr. Ryan said","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"he would step down in January .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"While the timing of his announcement was a surprise ,","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"lawmakers have been privately weighing the odds of the two front-runners , Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"( R. , Calif. )","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"and Majority Whip Steve Scalise","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"( R. , La . )","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"to replace him .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Mr. Ryan ' s planned departure could add to the headwinds","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"already buffeting the Republicans","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"as the midterm elections approach","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"because it is likely to weaken his power","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"to raise money for the party .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"\" This is a public acknowledgment","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"that the House is really , really gone , \"","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"said Dan Eberhart , a GOP donor and chief executive of a Colorado-based drilling services company .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"\" Ryan has unzipped a deluge of donors","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"that are now going to be focused more","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"than they were on the Senate . ' '","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Since 1994 , the president ' s party has lost an average of 23 seats in the House midterm elections .","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"The GOP this year is further burdened by President Donald Trump ' s low approval rating and the planned retirements by an unusually large number of House Republicans ,","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"although many are hoping","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"a strong economy will provide a boost for their party .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Mr. Ryan ' s announcement brings to 38 the number of House Republican incumbents","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"not seeking re-election ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"and the nonpartisan Cook Political Report Wednesday downgraded the chances","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"the GOP would hold his Wisconsin seat in the November election .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"The filing deadline is June 1 ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"so Mr. Ryan ' s decision allows some time","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"for another Republican to get in position","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"to run ;","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"two Democrats are already in the race ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"including one","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that has raised millions .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Democrats need a net gain of 23 House seats","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"to win the majority .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"They have identified many more targets than that ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"including 23 districts","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"now held by House Republicans","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that were captured by Democratic presidential nominee Hillary Clinton in 2016 .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"\" If the election were held next week ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"we ' d be in deep trouble , ' '","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"said former GOP House Speaker Newt Gingrich .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"\" As things stand right now ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"we would lose .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Our goal now is to wage a campaign","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"to change it . \"","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Some lawmakers were skeptical Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"that Mr. Ryan would be able to remain ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"as he plans ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"at the chamber ' s helm until January .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"\" It ' s tenable-I don ' t know","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"that it ' s probable , \"","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"said Rep. Mark Meadows","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"( R. , N.C. ) ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"chairman of the House Freedom Caucus , a group of conservative House Republicans","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"expected to play an influential role","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"in selecting the next House GOP leader .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Rep. Bradley Byrne","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"( R. , Ala. ) ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"who attended a lunch with the speaker Wednesday ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"if Mr. Ryan left early","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"it could \" jeopardize \" the party ' s chances","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"of keeping the majority this year .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"\" The last thing","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"we need have between now and the midterm elections is some sort of scramble","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"for who ' s going to be our leader , \"","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"How the House Could Change Hands","depth":2},{"id":77,"text":"Control of the U.S. House of Representatives turns on a handful of the 435 districts .","depth":3},{"id":78,"text":"Here ' s why those races are competitive .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"Mr. McCarthy is next in line","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"to succeed Mr. Ryan .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Lawmakers and House GOP aides said Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"the first question is whether the affable California Republican can sew up enough support .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Mr. McCarthy withdrew from the 2015 speaker race .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"He now has among the closest relationships of any lawmaker with Mr. Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"its isn ' t yet clear if conservatives will coalesce around him .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"His allies said","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"he has worked harder","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"and built stronger relationships with House Republicans since 2015 .","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"As the lawmaker in charge of scheduling bills for House floor votes , Mr. McCarthy has helped many of his colleagues score more minor legislative wins","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"that matter to them at home and on the campaign trail .","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"\" He ' s in a different spot","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"than where he was three years ago , \"","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"said Rep. Bill Huizenga","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"( R. , Mich. )","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"After Mr. McCarthy withdrew from the last race ,","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"\" he could have said","depth":16},{"id":97,"text":"' a pox upon all of you , '","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"and he didn ' t do that .","depth":16},{"id":99,"text":"He did the opposite . \"","depth":16},{"id":100,"text":"But conservatives ,","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"who had been previously suspicious of Mr. McCarthy ' s policy leanings ,","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"will play an even larger role","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"in selecting the next GOP leader ,","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"because so many centrist Republicans are planning to retire","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"and more could lose their seats in November .","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"If Mr. McCarthy ' s ascent again stalls ,","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"Mr. Scalise would likely become the lead candidate","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"to succeed Mr. Ryan .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"An increasingly frequent presence on national television , Mr. Scalise ' s national profile has soared","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"and his emotional connection with the House GOP intensified","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"after he survived a shooting of congressional Republicans at a baseball practice last June .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"Mr. Ryan didn ' t throw his support behind either of his deputies Wednesday ,","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"though he said","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"he would have more to say on the subject in the coming days .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"After spending nearly 20 years in Congress ,","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"Mr. Ryan said Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"that he had decided to leave","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"because he had accomplished many of his legislative goals","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"and did not want to be a \" Sunday dad \"","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"who only spent one day a week with his children in Wisconsin .","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"Mr. Ryan played a central role in the passage of the 2017 tax overhaul , Mr. Trump ' s biggest legislative achievement .","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"A former House Ways and Means Committee chairman , he sold the tax policies to sometimes-wary Republicans","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"and brokered for the necessary votes .","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"Its passage marked a personal redemption for him and congressional Republicans","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"after a bruising year","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"in which the House was barely able to achieve its long-sought repeal of the 2010 health law ,","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"and the effort ultimately faltered in the Senate .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"\" We have achieved a heck of a lot , \"","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"said Mr. Ryan ,","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"singling out the tax overhaul .","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"But he said","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"he had only agreed in the fall of 2015 to become the speaker reluctantly ,","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"and was no longer willing to be absent from home .","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"Mr. Ryan began pondering his retirement late last year ,","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"discussing his future with a small group of advisers and family ,","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"according to someone familiar with the decision .","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"He had been leaning toward retiring for a while ,","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"but made the final decision over the recent congressional recess ,","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"when his family joined him on a trip to Europe .","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"\" My dad died","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"when I was 16-the age","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"my daughter is , \"","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"said Mr. Ryan , 48 years old .","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"\" My kids aren ' t getting any younger","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"if I stay ,","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"they ' re only going to know me as a weekend dad . \"","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"Mr. Ryan has had an uneasy relationship with Mr. Trump .","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"He said Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"that Mr. Trump ' s victory in 2016 made it possible for the Republican House and Senate to enact the tax bill last year .","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"But he has split with Mr. Trump over many issues ,","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"taking a tougher tone on Russia ,","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"pushing for spending cuts to federal safety-net programs ,","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"and cautioning the president recently against pursuing steel tariffs ,","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"saying","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"they could lead to a trade war .","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"Mr. Trump tweeted Wednesday :","depth":7},{"id":158,"text":"\" Speaker Paul Ryan is a truly good man ,","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"while he will not be seeking re-election ,","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"he will leave a legacy of achievement","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"that nobody can question .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"We are with you Paul ! \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":327,"left":239,"right":326,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":189,"right":238,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":178,"right":188,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":172,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":170,"right":171,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":165,"right":169,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":169,"left":166,"right":168,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":166,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":4,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":177,"left":9,"right":176,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":176,"left":175,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":173,"right":174,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":173,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":182,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":180,"right":181,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":15,"right":179,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":184,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":183,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":20